# Content Creation System

This document describes the content authoring tools and workflows in ToolBoxAI-Solutions.

## Overview
- Create and edit lessons, quizzes, and assignments
- Upload media and resources
- Organize content into courses and modules

## Authoring Tools
- Rich text editor
- Media uploader
- Quiz builder
- Assignment manager

## Workflow
1. Create new content item
2. Add metadata and resources
3. Preview and test content
4. Publish to students

## Best Practices
- Use consistent formatting
- Test content before publishing
- Update content regularly
